This is a GPL implementation of a basic REST client API for Android. 
It handles all the different Http* objects from the Apache HttpClient
project and gives you a nice string output of the request's results.

Contributing: I'd like to know before you just start pushing stuff to
the repo. Send me an email at LinuxMercedes@gmail.com if you want to help.

